b'' b'' b'a friend of mine is seeing an acupuncturist and' b'wants to know if there is any danger of getting' b'aids from the needles.' b'' b'ask the practitioner whether he uses the pre-sterilized disposable' b'needles, or if he reuses needles, sterilizing them between use. in the' b"former case there's no conceivable way to get aids from the needles. in" b"the latter case it's highly unlikely (though many practitioners use the" b'disposable variety anyway).' b'' b'euclid' b'--' b'euclid k. standard disclaimers apply' b'"it is a bit ironic that we need the wave model [of light] to understand the' b'propagation of light only through that part of the system where it leaves no' b'trace." --hudson nelson (_university_physics_)' 